nodes.text: This planet was covered in mountains and seas that had a rainy climate. Rowan Freemaker and R0-GR hid the last Kyber Saber kyber crystal on this planet, until Naare found it.

This remote planet was located somewhere in the galaxy and was orbited by one moon. The planet's moon was later destroyed by Naare in 3 ABY. The planet was completely covered in mountains and seas but also had a rainy climate. The planet also had an atmosphere breathable to oxygen-breathers, such as humans.
